  <span id="freeText12685737284175182499" style="display:none">This book will break your heart, mend it and break it again (in a good way). This book will challenge long-held misconceptions about religion (in good way), and deliver a sweet, coming-of-age, romance story that is truly beautiful. I absolutely loved this story, so much so, that I do not know how many times I have read it. (Also, I cry every time I read it. So have tissues ready if you choose to read this delightful tale.) More importantly, this story reminds us that love is never wrong because that is the way God designed it to be. Give this story a chance. You will not be disappointed. <br />Sincerely, <br />Sassy Jacksun</span>
